  <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Multi-tiling sets, Riesz bases, and sampling near the critical density in LCA groups</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="260" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
